<TITLE>
Kwimu, the Loon (Qimu, Oqim, Kwemoo)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Kwimu (Qimu),
a loon who serves as messenger of the gods in Mi'kmaq and Passamaquoddy folklore.">
